WEBVTT

00:03:29.516 --> 00:03:32.324
I mean, what if you have
an illness or an infection?

00:03:32.348 --> 00:03:33.825
How can the doctor diagnose you

00:03:33.849 --> 00:03:36.711
without being able to see
the color change or inflammation?

00:03:36.735 --> 00:03:39.877
And what if everyone
is permanently invisible?

00:03:39.901 --> 00:03:42.140
Well, think about how boring
the world would be

00:03:42.164 --> 00:03:43.926
without seeing people on the streets,

00:03:43.950 --> 00:03:44.301
on TV,

00:03:44.325 --> 00:03:47.080
or at home on your computer

00:03:47.104 --> 00:03:48.859
like right now.

00:03:48.883 --> 00:03:51.290
It's lonely being invisible.

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:57.277
Now, which superpower physics lesson

00:03:57.301 --> 00:03:59.715
will you explore next?

00:03:59.739 --> 00:04:03.807
